{"text_id":169436,"tokens":["Post","-","Tra","umatic"," Slave"," Syndrome"," (","P","TSS",")"," is"," a"," term"," coined"," by"," Joy"," De","Gru","y","-","Le","Beau",","," a"," sociologist"," and"," therapist",","," to"," describe"," the"," lasting",","," detrimental"," effects"," of"," enslaved"," Africans"," and"," their"," descendants","."," It"," is"," a"," form"," of"," psychological"," trauma"," that"," can"," result"," from"," repeated"," exposure"," to"," trauma",","," suffering",","," and"," oppression",","," particularly"," in"," a"," systemic"," and"," institutional","ized"," manner",".","\n\n","The"," concept"," of"," P","TSS"," is"," rooted"," in"," the"," understanding"," that"," the"," trans","atlantic"," slave"," trade"," and"," the"," subsequent"," ongoing"," systemic"," racism"," and"," discrimination"," have"," created"," a"," legacy"," of"," trauma",","," which"," has"," been"," passed"," down"," from"," generation"," to"," generation","."," This"," trauma"," can"," manifest"," in"," a"," range"," of"," ways",","," including"," anxiety",","," depression",","," hyper","vigil","ance",","," and"," a"," general"," sense"," of"," power","lessness",".","\n\n","P","TSS"," is"," often"," referred"," to"," as"," the"," \"","slave"," syndrome","\""," or"," \"","PTS",",\""," and"," it"," is"," recognized"," as"," a"," form"," of"," complex"," trauma",","," which"," is"," characterized"," by"," a"," protracted"," and"," repeated"," exposure"," to"," a"," traumatic"," event"," or"," events","."," The"," trauma"," associated"," with"," slavery"," and"," racism"," has"," been"," compounded"," by"," the"," lack"," of"," control",","," agency",","," and"," social"," support",","," making"," it"," a"," particularly"," devastating"," and"," long","-","lasting"," experience",".","\n\n","The"," symptoms"," of"," P","TSS"," can"," vary"," widely",","," but"," common"," effects"," include",":","\n\n","*"," Hyper","vigil","ance"," and"," a"," heightened"," sense"," of"," threat","\n","*"," Height","ened"," start","le"," response","\n","*"," Increased"," anxiety"," and"," stress","\n","*"," Depression"," and"," affective"," flattening","\n","*"," Dis","sociation"," and"," dis","connection"," from"," emotions","\n","*"," Substance"," abuse"," and"," addiction","\n","*"," Interpersonal"," difficulties"," and"," challenges","\n\n","P","TSS"," has"," significant"," implications"," for"," the"," mental"," and"," physical"," health"," of"," African"," Americans",","," as"," well"," as"," their"," social"," and"," economic"," well","-","being","."," It"," can"," manifest"," in"," a"," range"," of"," contexts",","," including"," personal"," relationships",","," education",","," employment",","," and"," community"," engagement",".","\n\n","P","TSS"," is"," not"," unique"," to"," African"," Americans",","," as"," other"," communities"," and"," individuals"," who"," have"," experienced"," similar"," forms"," of"," trauma"," and"," oppression"," may"," also"," be"," affected","."," However",","," the"," historical"," and"," ongoing"," systemic"," nature"," of"," racism"," in"," the"," United"," States"," and"," elsewhere"," makes"," P","TSS"," a"," particularly"," relevant"," and"," important"," issue"," for"," African"," American"," communities",".","\n\n","Therapy",","," counseling",","," and"," other"," forms"," of"," treatment"," can"," help"," individuals"," overcome"," the"," effects"," of"," P","TSS","."," Additionally",","," community","-","based"," programs"," and"," initiatives"," aimed"," at"," promoting"," racial"," equity"," and"," social"," justice"," can"," help"," to"," address"," the"," root"," causes"," of"," P","TSS",".","\n\n","In"," recent"," years",","," P","TSS"," has"," been"," increasingly"," recognized"," as"," a"," legitimate"," psychological"," condition",","," and"," it"," has"," been"," included"," in"," various"," academic"," and"," professional"," contexts","."," However",","," more"," research"," and"," education"," are"," needed"," to"," fully"," understand"," the"," scope"," and"," impact"," of"," P","TSS",","," as"," well"," as"," to"," develop"," effective"," treatments"," and"," interventions","."],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}